{"text_id":41313,"tokens":["We"," present"," a"," comprehensive"," study"," on"," the"," detection"," of"," the"," Cosmic"," Far","-","Infrared"," Background"," (","CF","IRB",")"," radiation"," using"," the"," AK","ARI","/","Far","-","Infrared"," Surveyor"," (","FIS",")"," deep"," observations","."," The"," CF","IRB",","," a"," diffuse"," radiation"," field"," originating"," from"," the"," combined"," emission"," of"," distant"," galaxies",","," remains"," an"," elusive"," component"," in"," the"," cosmic"," electromagnetic"," spectrum","."," Despite"," its"," potential"," to"," provide"," insights"," into"," the"," evolution"," of"," galaxies"," and"," the"," formation"," of"," stars",","," the"," CF","IRB"," has"," been"," challenging"," to"," detect"," directly"," due"," to"," the"," dominant"," foreground"," emission"," from"," zodiac","al"," dust"," and"," Galactic"," cir","rus","."," Motiv","ated"," by"," the"," necessity"," to"," understand"," the"," build","-","up"," of"," the"," cosmic"," infrared"," background",","," we"," exploit"," the"," unique"," capabilities"," of"," AK","ARI","/","FIS"," to"," investigate"," the"," faint"," residual"," flux"," at"," far","-","infrared"," wavelengths","."," Our"," methodology"," involves"," the"," development"," of"," a"," sophisticated"," foreground"," subtraction"," technique",","," combining"," a"," likelihood"," analysis"," of"," the"," AK","ARI","/","FIS"," data"," with"," a"," priori"," information"," from"," complementary"," observations","."," We"," demonstrate"," the"," effectiveness"," of"," our"," approach"," by"," detecting"," the"," CF","IRB"," signal"," in"," the"," AK","ARI","/","FIS"," deep"," fields",","," providing"," new"," insights"," into"," the"," properties"," of"," the"," CF","IRB"," and"," its"," implications"," for"," galaxy"," evolution"," models","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-70b","label":1}